    <div class='bann-col'>
      <div class='bann-text-hold'>
        <p>Elevate your product with expert design. Partner with Eleken for seamless UI/UX solutions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='bann-col bann-col-flex'>
      <a href='../ui-ux-design-services' class='bann-btn' target='_blank'>
        <span>Learn more</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div></div><h2>What is a sales deck?</h2><p><strong>A sales deck is a presentation that sales teams use to introduce a product or service to potential clients.</strong> It’s also important to mention that sales presentation and pitch decks are not the same, though the two terms are often used interchangeably. Unlike a pitch deck, which targets investors, sales decks focus on demonstrating product value and <a href="designing-a-sales-funnel-for-saas-that-delivers-results-for-your-business">moving leads through the sales funnel</a>.</p><p>You may find more information of <a href="pitch-deck-examples">pitch deck and their examples</a> in our recent article. And for now it’s tile to move to sales presentation examples.</p><h2>Some good sales pitch deck examples</h2><p>Here are 27 best sales decks from various businesses over the years. They&#x27;re not perfect, but each one has something valuable to teach us about creating presentations that work. Let&#x27;s see what makes them special.</p><h3>1. Stripe </h3><div class="w-embed"><div class="wrap-slider-blog">
      <div class="swiper">
        <div class="swiper-wrapper">
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a1618ca61ec9a3085875_1.01.webp" 
alt="An image of a Stripe logo"></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a16326ae7fbd08edd0d2_1.02.webp" alt="An Stripe image with text The new standard in online payments"></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a16233c1e000eaf32586_1.03.webp" alt="Four icons on white background with text on it"></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a163461eb55ecd07a12f_1.04.webp" alt="An image with some logos and text You’re in good company"></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a16267ebeee14bcbbfa9_1.05.webp" alt="An image with text Global natives and Stripe logo"></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a16222bf60f4b6e5ea1f_1.06.webp" alt="The pixture with a purple background and with text on it"></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a162384b39fd70d1aeb3_1.07.webp" alt="An image with text The new payment stack"></div>
