          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a1635b2e8445c3223897_1.09.webp" alt="A picture with text Removing financial complexity"></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a1643ac79a49447d0509_1.10.webp" alt="An image with people on it and Stripe logo"></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a1640ca94163e583ad1c_1.11.webp" alt="An image with a quote on it and Stripe logo"></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a164591cfedbaec3d20d_1.12.webp" alt="The picture with Stripe logo and text Let’s grow the internet economy together"></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a164809a4953cdbd39d9_1.13.webp" alt="An image with text Guides and resources"></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a164cb896adced5b3792_1.14.webp" alt="An image with people on it"></div>
