          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src=" https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a174591cfedbaec3df62_2.15.webp" alt="An eagle in the sky and some text"></div>
