          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src="
https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e8b3356a5a8f5321855bbe7/6751a1b4977e10edd966617c_5.02.webp" alt="Description of the problem we faced"></div>
          <div class="swiper-slide"><img class="slider-blog-image" src="
